{"tid":1694893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「真心求集氣」科大男生情況仍然危殆 病況嚴重且不斷惡化 生命危在旦夕","createTime":"2019-11-05T10:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T11:01:39.000Z","uid":113368,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"46e324270ceddac65b847e59de23330c43beb9e8","tid":1694893,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"【18:00】據悉，科大男生情況仍然危殆，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>病況嚴重且不斷惡化</strong></span></span>；腦部經過兩次手術、切除部份顳葉後，創傷、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>內出血情況未受控、顱內壓亦很高，生命危在旦夕</strong></span></span>，但尚未證實腦幹死亡，亦無人提出拔喉意願。另有消息指，病人有電解質失衡、瞳孔放大，正接受強心針等維生治療，以控制血壓等。由於病人臨床情況不斷改變，據了解臨床心理學家一直與病人家屬溝通，盡量提供即時協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191105&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60232901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191105%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60232901&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=0dcc07d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191105%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60232901&h=3ccee2d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191105&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60232901</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>求各位唔好再講荷蘭叻住 一齊同周同學集氣先啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4514e7900b7d3ec0f0e5195db2cbf2862b1a3a2e","tid":1694893,"uid":113368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"求大家了 藍絲廢老重要得過手足條命咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a13a0cfe69ab5197a154e5271913c682efa689","tid":1694893,"uid":260065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:28:11.000Z","msg"